SUMMARY:Waystone Warhammer 40\,000 RTT
DTSTAMP:20260403T051046Z
DTSTART:20260404T170000Z
DESCRIPTION:A ten-person organized play event for Warhammer 40\,000 using t
	he current Grand Tournament mission rules with awards and prizes!  Sign up
	 here. Members receive 48-hour priority access as well as 20% off admissio
	n at checkout. What is an RTT? RTT stands for "Rogue Trader Tournament". T
	his is just another way of saying "small tournament" \\(as opposed to a Gr
	and Tournament\, or GT\\). They're great for simply getting in a full day 
	of games\, practicing for larger events\, or to experiment with new army c
	ompositions.\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/waystone-war
